{"tid":990842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾球員賤種朗 真正垃圾實力update 20190122","createTime":"2019-01-22T02:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T04:53:41.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"31c064eb048de505efef0e5f8dd43382488886e2","tid":990842,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾朗對弱隊基爾禾都廢到不堪入目.....</span><br />\n<br />\n本週<br />\n賤種朗 - 8射0入 (仲要炒12M)<br />\n美斯 - 2射1入<br />\n<br />\n#數據post目的係唔想班賤朗迷再呃人<br />\n#上述數據由今季第1場比賽開始計算<br />\n#上述數據根據 who scored + 7m 賽後數據 每場累積而來<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 133射14入球 (4球靠12碼) (10.5%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n意大利社區盾 6射1入 (16.6%)<br />\n意大利盃: n射0入 (190113vs 榜尾博洛尼亞, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n<br />\n已射166球 得個16個入球 合共9.6%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 82射18入球 (1球靠12碼) (21.9%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n西班牙盃: n射1入 (190118vs 中游利雲特, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n102射入25球 合共24.5%"},{"pid":"e3c8f2f5385386d5e399de0464a851e688d08a73","tid":990842,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/22/d/d219e856d2e55f11cf50a29bfde9ee1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F22%2Fd%2Fd219e856d2e55f11cf50a29bfde9ee1e.jpg&h=004c0a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十二碼好難射</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/22/8/82be3fef2791690c0068a9247b121e20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F22%2F8%2F82be3fef2791690c0068a9247b121e20.jpg&h=0879ab10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span styl